<h3><b>List</b></h3>
<h4>+ Use</h4>
<h4>The list is composed of the global list + the list item, so we will see the usage for the list and the list item, then the </h4>
<ul>
    <li>
        <b>with twig extension:</b>
            <pre>
{{ "{{ alamanach_list($content, $framework, $order = 'default', $decoration = 'default', $class = [], $attributes = [], $tag = null, $link = null) }}"|e }}</pre>
    </li>
    <li>
        <b>with twig embed:</b>
            <pre>
{{ "{% embed 'AlmanachBundle:bricks/' ~ framework ~ ':_list.html.twig' with {content: content, framework: framework, ... } only %}"|e }}
{{ "    {% block content %}"|e }}
{{ "        {# content #}"|e }}
{{ "    {% endblock %}"|e }}
{{ "{% endembed %}"|e }}</pre>
    </li>
</ul>
<br><h4>+ parameters:</h4>
<ul>
    <li>
        <b>content</b>: content of your list.
    </li>
    <li>
        <b>framework</b>: framework you are using.
        <ul>
            <li>bootstrap</li>
            <li>foundation</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
        <b>order</b>: order of your list.
        <ul>
            <li>default</li>
            <li>ordered</li>
            <li>unordered</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
        <b>decoration</b>: decoration of your list.
        <ul>
            <li>default</li>
            <li>inline</li>
            <li>unstyled</li>
            <li>disc</li>
            <li>square</li>
            <li>circle</li>
            <li>nothing</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
<h4>+ example</h4>

<ul style="list-style-type: none">
    <li>
        {% embed 'AlmanachBundle:bricks/' ~ framework ~ ':_list.html.twig' with {framework: framework, order: 'unordered', decoration: 'disc'} only %}
            {% block content %}
                {% embed 'AlmanachBundle:bricks/' ~ framework ~ ':_listItem.html.twig' with {framework: framework} only %}
                    {% block content %}
                        Unordered list disc
                    {% endblock %}
                {% endembed %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}
    </li>
    <li>
    {{ almanach_list([
        almanach_listItem('Title' ~ almanach_list([
            almanach_listItem('Content 1', framework),
            almanach_listItem('Content 2', framework),
            almanach_listItem('Content 3', framework),
        ],
        framework, 'default', 'disc'),framework),
    ],
    framework,
    'default',
    'square'
    ) }}
    </li>
</ul>